oth jeans and chinos, making them a versatile addition to any wardrobe.","id":142,"images":["https://i.imgur.com/sC0ztOB.jpeg","https://i.imgur.com/Jf9DL9R.jpeg","https://i.imgur.com/R1IN95T.jpeg"],"price":39,"slug":"classic-blue-suede-casual-shoes","title":"Classic Blue Suede Casual Shoes","updatedAt":"2026-03-02T20:06:48.000Z"},{"category":{"creationAt":"2026-03-02T20:06:42.000Z","id":17,"image":"https://i.imgur.com/BG8J0Fj.jpg","name":"Miscellaneous","slug":"miscellaneous","updatedAt":"2026-03-02T20:06:42.000Z"},"creationAt":"2026-03-02T20:06:48.000Z","description":"This modern electric bicycle combines style and efficiency with its unique design and top-notch performance features. Equipped with a durable frame, enhanced battery life, and integrated tech capabilities, it's perfect for the eco-conscious commuter looking to navigate the city with ease.","id":143,"images":["https://i.imgur.com/BG8J0Fj.jpg","https://i.imgur.com/ujHBpCX.jpg","https://i.imgur.com/WHeVL9H.jpg"],"price":22,"slug":"sleek-futuristic-electric-bicycle","title":"Sleek Futuristic Electric Bicycle","updatedAt":"2026-03-02T20:06:48.000Z"},{"category":{"creationAt":"2026-03-02T20:06:42.000Z","id":17,"image":"https://i.imgur.com/BG8J0Fj.jpg","name":"Miscellaneous","slug":"miscellaneous","updatedAt":"2026-03-02T20:06:42.000Z"},"creationAt":"2026-03-02T20:06:48.000Z","description":"Elevate your style with our Chic Transparent Fashion Handbag, perfect for showcasing your essentials with a clear, modern edge. This trendy accessory features durable acrylic construction, luxe gold-tone hardware, and an elegant chain strap. Its compact size ensures you can carry your day-to-day items with ease and sophistication.","id":144,"images":["https://i.imgur.com/Lqaqz59.jpg","https://i.imgur.com/uSqWK0m.jpg","https://i.imgur.com/atWACf1.jpg"],"price":61,"slug":"chic-transparent-fashion-handbag","title":"Chic Transparent Fashion Handbag","updatedAt":"2026-03-02T20:06:48.000Z"},{"category":{"creationAt":"2026-03-02